Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神所眷顧的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對流逝著的時間的人  很容易忘卻生活的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  只要心裡有相信些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣就絕對不會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.39,0:02:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰在…叫我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:27.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能贏我們小狼君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個領主的秘術很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.55,0:03:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領主父子利用這種力量  統治著這個城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  對方只有兩個人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.22,0:03:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果鎮上的人團結起來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該可以和他們對抗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有對抗過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大約半年前  鎮上的人都聚集在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和領主父子展開了戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  領主的城裡到處佈滿了秘術
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也不能靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.98,0:04:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個秘術就是摩可拿說過的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處都充滿了神秘的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽毛的波動我也越來越感覺不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們無法進城的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就等領主從城裡出來就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領主是絕對不會出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那樣的話  打他兒子的主意如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他捉來做人質怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉來做人質？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才若無其事的說了句挺沒有人性的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:36.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙用秘術監視著整個城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像昨天小狼君被風襲擊那樣是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是只有攻城一條路了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  關鍵在於主將吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有很好的指揮的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:56.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼攻城也不會攻破
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:05:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個城鎮裡那麼善戰的人…根本沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不是有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能幫我們嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑碰這次真是格外的熱情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是對「那個」厭倦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.06,0:05:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修理屋頂你一個人做就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:27.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定去攻領主的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.79,0:05:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  我需要一些士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.84,0:05:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事的話  我還是心裡有數的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小丫頭好像又要搞什麼鬼花樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城裡的防守萬無一失  不用管她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  為什麼我們要放任春香不管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.47,0:05:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個丫頭將來可能會是你的妻子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:05:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.37,0:06:05.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香她有遠超她母親的潛能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們一族要得到那股力量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼把她娶進家來是最好的捷徑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在有了這個  就已經沒有那個必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽了這話我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:33.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天  春香也會像她娘一樣逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.73,0:06:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母女一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那個世界相見就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進去就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.42,0:07:00.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是我的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.76,0:07:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.39,0:07:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是不服從領主的統治
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.77,0:07:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而暗中決定戰鬥的城中勇士秘密聚集的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音是春香嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空汰和嵐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們認識嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是初次見面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這個是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是「這個」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是摩可拿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩…摩可拿？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然長得有點怪  但也是我的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:54.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LOVE  LOVE？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L…LOVE  LOVE？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:08:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們互相喜歡對方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天會結為夫妻的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是那樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  嘻嘻嘻…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是  我有事拜託你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  我們認識的那兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和眼前的這兩個人  靈魂雖然是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.26,0:08:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在這個世界裡卻過著不同的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎  公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  多少有點明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止戰鬥？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再說了  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:45.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是和大家商量後做出的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.81,0:08:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半年前的戰鬥  我們慘敗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  我們是不可能贏得了秘術的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…雖然很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:49.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們不能再讓人犧牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:01.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要進去…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:27.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母…母親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:41.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我作對的人  都不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽的靈魂將無法升天入地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能永遠飄蕩在荒蕪的異世界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親  母親
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻攔我的人都除掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個城鎮是我的了  哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想獲得力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人也能為母親報仇的那種強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.02,0:11:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  你在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  沒能幫上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:54.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家因為半年前的那一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喪失了繼續戰鬥的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  理解了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:12.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.07,0:12:15.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要進去…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:35.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.89,0:12:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.25,0:12:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻  不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:43.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果進去這扇門就再也出不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼  別進去！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小狼進去出不來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮上的人會傷心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再有人犧牲了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.47,0:13:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要進去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:26.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且  一定把小櫻也帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.31,0:14:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部的城門有八個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:11.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是得集中突破其中的一個才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.10,0:14:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡發什麼呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.24,0:14:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲的時候認真點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意見的話  黑碰自己來幹就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻城之前哪裡有心思修房頂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:37.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是秘術呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:41.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼和小櫻…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:15:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻城之前居然就這麼自作主張…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.61,0:15:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城堡內的秘術  比想像中的還要強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進了門的話  就沒法再出來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果聽到我的聲音的話  就請回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:57.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:15:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:15:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.19,0:16:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是  篝火攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.83,0:16:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是巨岩攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了  公主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.02,0:16:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:19.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  下面讓他們嘗嘗什麼苦頭比較好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.21,0:17:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.93,0:17:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香那丫頭好像說了什麼奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮裡的人們都聚集起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的話？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再說任性的話了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被門吸進去的話  從來沒有能回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻是神所眷顧的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  一定會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香說的  會是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:17:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果是真的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:14.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.36,0:18:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻公主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可憐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:34.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了嗎  我們的聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於有人注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…都是鎮上的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.40,0:19:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.30,0:19:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那之後一直在這個異世界裡生活著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺  就變成這個樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:01.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.71,0:20:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  請放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能解開秘術的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:09.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們一定能恢復成原來的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對外貌變醜陋了的他們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你仍能沒有任何懼意地去撫摸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.53,0:20:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是神所眷顧的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有著神的祝福的女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.94,0:20:39.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就請勇敢地去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和所愛的人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返回那應該回去的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.22,0:21:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.27,0:21:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻也在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.17,0:21:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.63,0:21:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.69,0:21:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩真的是神所眷顧的女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信著你們會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙為什麼能夠出來？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來那些傢伙們  來歷並不簡單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.90,0:21:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:22:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  結果還是沒有什麼攻城行動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.62,0:22:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.48,0:22:06.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  鎮上的人們的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.85,0:22:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像發生了一些變化哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.07,0:22:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒領主的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.67,0:22:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吸進門裡的同伴們  就能回來了是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.35,0:22:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這麼說的話  那就一定要去戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.52,0:22:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.61,0:22:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說服大家的話  還需要一些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我的好消息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.83,0:22:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  蘇醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.84,0:22:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不祥的邪惡公主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.01,0:22:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.64,0:22:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘妖
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.65,0:24:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在邪惡的領主那裡  可能會有羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.48,0:24:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼猜測的小狼他們
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.06,0:24:38.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算進入領主的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.11,0:24:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是城堡被秘術保護怎麼也進不去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.70,0:24:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是請不要擔心哦
